{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.1","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 4:1","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.003.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.004.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-6: cf. 1 Pi 3:18. Ro 6:6-13. \u00c9p 4:17-24.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.4.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Ainsi donc, Christ ayant souffert dans la chair, vous aussi armez-vous de la m\u00eame pens\u00e9e. Car celui qui a souffert dans la chair en a fini avec le p\u00e9ch\u00e9,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4","name":"1 Pierre 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.2","name":"1 Pierre 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.22","name":"1 Pierre 3:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.2","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 4:2","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.004.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.004.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.4.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>afin de vivre, non plus selon les convoitises des hommes, mais selon la volont\u00e9 de Dieu, pendant le temps qui lui reste \u00e0 vivre dans la chair.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4","name":"1 Pierre 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.3","name":"1 Pierre 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.1","name":"1 Pierre 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.3","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 4:3","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.004.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.004.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.4.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>C\u2019est assez, en effet, d\u2019avoir dans le temps pass\u00e9 accompli la volont\u00e9 des pa\u00efens, en marchant dans la dissolution, les convoitises, l\u2019ivrognerie, les exc\u00e8s du manger et du boire, et les idol\u00e2tries criminelles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4","name":"1 Pierre 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.4","name":"1 Pierre 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.2","name":"1 Pierre 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.4","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 4:4","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.004.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.004.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.4.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Aussi trouvent-ils \u00e9trange que vous ne vous pr\u00e9cipitiez pas avec eux dans le m\u00eame d\u00e9bordement de d\u00e9bauche, et ils vous calomnient.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4","name":"1 Pierre 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.5","name":"1 Pierre 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.3","name":"1 Pierre 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.5","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 4:5","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.004.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.004.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.4.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Ils rendront compte \u00e0 celui qui est pr\u00eat \u00e0 juger les vivants et les morts.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4","name":"1 Pierre 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.6","name":"1 Pierre 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.4","name":"1 Pierre 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.6","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 4:6","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.004.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.004.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.4.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Car l\u2019\u00c9vangile a \u00e9t\u00e9 aussi annonc\u00e9 aux morts, afin que, apr\u00e8s avoir \u00e9t\u00e9 jug\u00e9s comme les hommes quant \u00e0 la chair, ils vivent selon Dieu quant \u00e0 l\u2019Esprit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4","name":"1 Pierre 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.7","name":"1 Pierre 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.5","name":"1 Pierre 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.7","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 4:7","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.004.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.004.008,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 7-11: cf. Lu 21:34-36. Ga 6:10. (Ro 12:5-11. 1 Co 10:31.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.4.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>\n    La fin de toutes choses est proche. Soyez donc sages et sobres, pour vaquer \u00e0 la pri\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4","name":"1 Pierre 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.8","name":"1 Pierre 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.6","name":"1 Pierre 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.8","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 4:8","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.004.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.004.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.4.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Avant tout, ayez les uns pour les autres une ardente charit\u00e9, car<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    La charit\u00e9 couvre une multitude de p\u00e9ch\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4","name":"1 Pierre 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.9","name":"1 Pierre 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.7","name":"1 Pierre 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.9","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 4:9","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.004.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.004.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"1Pet.4.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Exercez l\u2019hospitalit\u00e9 les uns envers les autres, sans murmures.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4","name":"1 Pierre 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.10","name":"1 Pierre 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.8","name":"1 Pierre 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.10","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 4:10","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.004.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.004.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"1Pet.4.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Comme de bons dispensateurs des diverses gr\u00e2ces de Dieu, que chacun de vous mette au service des autres le don qu\u2019il a re\u00e7u,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4","name":"1 Pierre 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.11","name":"1 Pierre 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.9","name":"1 Pierre 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.11","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 4:11","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.004.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.004.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"1Pet.4.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Si quelqu\u2019un parle, que ce soit comme annon\u00e7ant les oracles de Dieu; si quelqu\u2019un remplit un minist\u00e8re, qu\u2019il le remplisse selon la force que Dieu communique, afin qu\u2019en toutes choses Dieu soit glorifi\u00e9 par J\u00e9sus-Christ, \u00e0 qui appartiennent la gloire et la puissance, aux si\u00e8cles des si\u00e8cles. Amen!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4","name":"1 Pierre 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.12","name":"1 Pierre 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.10","name":"1 Pierre 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.12","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 4:12","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.004.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.004.013,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 12-19: cf. Mt 5:10-12. Ac 5:41; 14:22. 2 Th 1:4-12.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.4.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Bien-aim\u00e9s, ne soyez pas surpris, comme d\u2019une chose \u00e9trange qui vous arrive, de la fournaise qui est au milieu de vous pour vous \u00e9prouver.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4","name":"1 Pierre 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.13","name":"1 Pierre 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.11","name":"1 Pierre 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.13","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 4:13","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.004.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.004.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.4.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>R\u00e9jouissez-vous, au contraire, de la part que vous avez aux souffrances de Christ, afin que vous soyez aussi dans la joie et dans l\u2019all\u00e9gresse lorsque sa gloire appara\u00eetra.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4","name":"1 Pierre 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.14","name":"1 Pierre 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.12","name":"1 Pierre 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.14","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 4:14","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.004.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.004.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.4.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Si vous \u00eates outrag\u00e9s pour le nom de Christ, vous \u00eates heureux, parce que l\u2019Esprit de gloire, l\u2019Esprit de Dieu, repose sur vous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4","name":"1 Pierre 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.15","name":"1 Pierre 4:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.13","name":"1 Pierre 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.15","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 4:15","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.004.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.004.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.4.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Que nul de vous, en effet, ne souffre comme meurtrier, ou voleur, ou malfaiteur, ou comme s\u2019ing\u00e9rant dans les affaires d\u2019autrui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4","name":"1 Pierre 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.16","name":"1 Pierre 4:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.14","name":"1 Pierre 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.16","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 4:16","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.004.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.004.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.4.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Mais si quelqu\u2019un souffre comme chr\u00e9tien, qu\u2019il n\u2019en ait point honte, et que plut\u00f4t il glorifie Dieu \u00e0 cause de ce nom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4","name":"1 Pierre 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.17","name":"1 Pierre 4:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.15","name":"1 Pierre 4:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.17","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 4:17","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.004.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.004.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.4.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Car c\u2019est le moment o\u00f9 le jugement va commencer par la maison de Dieu. Or, si c\u2019est par nous qu\u2019il commence, quelle sera la fin de ceux qui n\u2019ob\u00e9issent pas \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9vangile de Dieu?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4","name":"1 Pierre 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.18","name":"1 Pierre 4:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.16","name":"1 Pierre 4:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.18","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 4:18","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.004.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.004.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.4.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Et si le juste se sauve avec peine, que deviendront l\u2019impie et le p\u00e9cheur?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4","name":"1 Pierre 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.19","name":"1 Pierre 4:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.17","name":"1 Pierre 4:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.19","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 4:19","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.004.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.005.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.4.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Ainsi, que ceux qui souffrent selon la volont\u00e9 de Dieu remettent leurs \u00e2mes au fid\u00e8le Cr\u00e9ateur, en faisant ce qui est bien.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4","name":"1 Pierre 4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.1","name":"1 Pierre 5:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.18","name":"1 Pierre 4:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbc616ad9.64762810');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbc616ad9.64762810\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbc616ad9.64762810","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbc616ad9.64762810'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbc616ad9.64762810\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}